definition: Slovakia/Slovak/abbr. for 斯洛伐克[Si1 luo4 fa2 ke4]

sentences.english: The Kansas City broadband plan is well advanced.
sentences.chinese: 堪萨斯城宽频项目如今进展顺利。

sentences.english: In Topeka , Kansas, it is illegal to drive ones car through a parade.
sentences.chinese: 在堪萨斯州的托皮卡，开车穿过游行队伍也是违法的。

sentences.english: And Kansas she says is the name of the star.
sentences.chinese: 她说堪萨斯是那颗星星的名字。

sentences.english: 4，Toto，I＇ve got a feeling we＇re not in Kansas anymore.
sentences.chinese: 托托，我想我们再也回不去堪萨斯了。

sentences.english: Only a surging Kansas City Royals team buoyed my spirits.
sentences.chinese: 只有刚出道不久的堪萨斯皇家棒球队能鼓舞我的精神。

sentences.english: Finally, he called the name of the senator from Kansas.
sentences.chinese: 最后，首席大法官叫到了这位堪萨斯州参议员的名字。

sentences.english: Much of Greensburg, Kansas has been leveled by a tornado.
sentences.chinese: 差不多整个堪萨斯州的格林斯堡都被龙卷风推平了。

sentences.english: And then moving to Topeka, Kansas.
sentences.chinese: 然后，移民到堪萨斯州的托贝卡。

sentences.english: The Jayhawks led by 17 at the break.
sentences.chinese: 在中场休息时，堪萨斯松鹰领先了17分。

sentences.english: She was not sure how it ended up in Kansas.
sentences.chinese: 但她也搞不清这封信为何最后跑到了堪萨斯州。

sentences.english: In the end, the Kansas Supreme Court ruling stands.
sentences.chinese: 堪萨斯法院的判决为终审判决。

sentences.english: Hinrich at the University of Kansas is the most glorious period in his senior year.
sentences.chinese: 辛里奇在堪萨斯大学最辉煌的时期是在他大四的那年。

sentences.english: The good old Kansas wind can do it on its own.
sentences.chinese: 堪萨斯的自然风就能把这事办好。

sentences.english: Final exams at Kansas University are only a few weeks away.
sentences.chinese: 堪萨斯州大学的期末考试刚刚过去几个星期。

sentences.english: Business delegates will visit a coffee roaster in Kansas City.
sentences.chinese: 商界代表们将参观堪萨斯城的一家咖啡烘烤店。

sentences.english: Kansas is hardly a hotbed of eco-activism.
sentences.chinese: 堪萨斯州算不上生态主义的热土。
